Package: thermoservice
Architecture: all
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends},	${misc:Depends}, python3-flask, gunicorn
Description: Temperature sharing service for DS18B20
 Show current temerature on 0.0.0.0:5000

Package: thermometer-zabbix
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, thermoservice, zabbix-agent2 | zabbix-agent
Description: Zabbix Agent integration for DS18B20 thermometer
 This package provides Zabbix Agent configuration for monitoring
 DS18B20 temperature sensors. It enables Zabbix to collect temperature
 data using the thermo command.
 .
 Works with both zabbix-agent and zabbix-agent2.
 .
 After installation, the following user parameters are available:
  - sensor.temp.value: Current temperature in Celsius
  - sensor.temp.celsius: Current temperature in Celsius
